data.title: How to Clean Bathtubs | Mr. Clean®
data.description:
Wondering how to clean bathtub grime once and for all? Mr. Clean’s best bathroom cleaner is the Mr. Clean Magic Eraser Foaming Bath Scrubber with Febreze Meadows & Rain. It’s specially textured and infused with a foaming cleanser for more bathroom cleaning power. The Mr. Clean Magic Eraser removes soap scum and bathtub rings quickly (and is also a great shower cleaner). So if you like it but you don’t want to put a ring on it, there’s no clean like Mr. Clean.

This Mr. Clean tutorial video demonstrates how to clean bathtub dirt and grime easily using the Mr. Clean Magic Eraser Foaming Bath Scrubber.

Test a small area with light pressure before use. Not recommended for the following surfaces: high gloss, polished, dark, brushed, satin, faux, bare/polished wood, copper, stainless steel appliances, non-stick coating or vehicle body. Rinse required for surfaces in direct contact with food. Do not use with chlorine bleach or other household cleaners. Do not use on skin or other body parts. Using on skin will likely cause abrasions. Avoid contact with eyes. May cause eye irritation. Keep out of reach of toddlers and pets to avoid accidental ingestion.
